text.tspan: On centre and corner squares of the board:
Players take turns in order until there is a winner
Move: Top piece of 1 stack moves 1 square,
from the centre to a side square, or
from a side square to the centre
Winner: A player who at any time
a tree or nest on the board
Each player gets 2 random private cards
Remaining cards form a face down pile
Action: A move or a card swap
Card swap: Player taking the turn
swaps either of their cards for a random
